==VOLUME==          

Displays detailed information about system volumes.
[[code format="text"]]
  CSI     DCL             Operation
  ---     ---             ---------
  /F      /FULL           Display detailed listing
  /V      /VERIFY         Check structure without display
[[code]]
Example:
[[code format="text"]]
  .r volume
  sy:/v           ! verify system disk okay
[[code]]
* For more information see [[Analyse_Command|ANALYSE VOLUME]] and [[Show_Command|SHOW VOLUME]].


